title: Hum Hain Kamaal Ke
subTitle: Two men with hearing and speech impairments run a grocery store. When a man is murdered in their store by an underworld gang who are after stolen diamonds, they try their hand at solving the case.

title: Jai Mahashakti
subTitle: The king of Travancore is ruthless and tortures his subjects. However, Vaikundasamy, an incarnation of Lord Vishnu, decides to put an end to this tyranny.

title: Sri Ram Mandir
subTitle: Gopanna, a devotee of Lord Rama, goes through various trials and tribulations while collecting funds to construct a temple. He receives help from his deity throughout his journey.

title: Sandwich
subTitle: Sher Singh has two wives, Nisha and Sweety, and juggles his time between them. However, when his two wives cross paths, his troubles increase manifold leading to hilarious situations.

title: Bruce Lee: The Fighter
subTitle: Kartik sacrifices his studies for his sister and becomes a stunt man. But he ends up helping a cop to unearth the evil designs of Deepak.

title: Aa Ab Laut Chalein
subTitle: After graduating from a university in India, an unemployed man decides to try his luck in New York and gets caught in a love triangle between an equally unlucky girl and a rich girl.

title: Ladaai
subTitle: A man is wrongly accused and jailed for 18 years. After completing his jail term, he confronts the judge who convicted him and asks her to find the real culprits.

title: Indian
subTitle: Police officer Raj Azad arrests terrorist Wasim Khan and prepares to interrogate him. However, his father-in-law mysteriously dies, after which he is blamed for his death and goes on the run.

title: Andhaa Kanoon
subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Andhaa Kanoon

title: Double Gadbad
subTitle: A series of comical complexities ensue when two men who look alike find themselves in numerous problems, leading to utter confusion.

title: Adharm
subTitle: Mr Verma's decision to disown his son Jaggan sparks a vow of retribution. Years later, Jaggan devises a plan to destroy his family and retaliate against his father.

title: Love U Ganesha
subTitle: Chintu always complains to Lord Ganesha about the hard work that he has to do as a fifth-grader. Lord Ganesha decides to help him in his own unique way.

title: Ganga Tere Desh Mein
subTitle: After arresting and institutionalising a notorious criminal who has lost his mental faculties, inspector Ajay finds his mother feeding the criminal. But when he digs deeper he uncovers a tragic truth.

title: Karma
subTitle: Accompanied by a troubled trio of prisoners, a high-ranking law enforcement officer sets out to avenge the miseries inflicted upon his family by an anti-national group.

title: Phool Bane Angaray
subTitle: After her husband, Ranjit, a police officer, is killed by the corrupt and powerful Bishamber, Namrata pledges to avenge his death and bring him justice.

title: S 3
subTitle: A police officer is assigned to solve the murder of the police commissioner. However, when he stumbles across a criminal syndicate, he decides to put an end to their tyranny.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Kabzaa
subTitle: Ravi works for Veljibhai Soda, a gangster, and does illegal work for him. Once, he is asked to vacate Ali from his property, but he gets inspired by his ideals and decides to change his ways.

title: I Killed Bapu
subTitle: Nathuram Godse becomes one of the most hated men in the country after he assassinates Mahatma Gandhi. When he has his day in court, he explains his thoughts and motivations behind the crime.

title: Main Hoon Durga
subTitle: Durgi lives happily with her family until a few men rape her sister and even kill her father. Agitated, she decides to seek revenge.

title: Maharaja
subTitle: Prince Kohinoor returns home after twenty years only to discover that Ranbir Singh, his parents' killer, still holds control. Subsequently, he decides to defeat him to protect his loved ones.

title: Rudrangi
subTitle: Bheem Rao Deshmukh, a tyrant who oppresses his people, is drawn to a beautiful woman named Rudrangi and desires physical contact with her. In order to satisfy his obsession, he terrorises her village.

title: Aitraaz
subTitle: When a company chairman's trophy wife stirs up a storm in a happily married employee's life, the tumultuous winds drag all of them into an intense courtroom showdown.

title: Phool Aur Angaar
subTitle: A young man rescues a woman from being molested but gets accused of the heinous crime instead. Trying to apprehend the miscreants, he gets caught in a web of deception and lies.

title: Badal
subTitle: Badal's family dies at the hands of a corrupt police officer. While he is raised by his father's friend, he turns into a terrorist and vows to avenge his family's death.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.
